              },
              "free_text": [
                " Spallation reaction in a mercury target",
                "irradiated with 3-GeV protons (150 kW) . The proton",
                "beams were supplied at a repetition rate of 25 Hz and",
                "in the \"double-bunch mode\". Produced neutrons were",
                "slowed down in a supercritical para hydrogen moderator."
              ]
            }
          ],
